text: Selles is the name of seven communes in France: * Selles, Eure, in the Eure department * Selles, Marne, in the Marne department * Selles, Pas-de-Calais, in the Pas-de-Calais department * Selles, Haute-Saône, in the Haute-Saône department * Selles-Saint-Denis, in the Loir-et-Cher department * Selles-sur- Cher, in the Loir-et-Cher department * Selles-sur-Nahon, in the Indre department == Other == * Selles-sur-Cher cheese, a French goats' milk cheese
title: Selles
